item.title: Florida Gulf Coast University
item.description: Florida Gulf Coast University, located in Fort Myers, is a Florida public university, offering undergraduate and graduate degree programs. FGCU has centers throughout Southwest Florida including Port Charlotte, Cape Coral, and Naples. FGCU is accredited by the Commission on Colleges of the Southern Association of Colleges and Schools (SACS).
